{
  "texts": [
    "They make use of an existing theory-driven value dictionary and perform an extensive validity study on the proposed evaluation procedure.",
    "The requirement for the suitability of tests for LLMs (R3) is the most addressed concern across all studies.",
    "This is due to the fact that we consider the utilization of a test with a suitable input and output format to be an appropriate effort.",
    "The requirement is considered fulfilled if the selected test has been originally designed in an appropriate format.",
    "Exceptions to this are, for example, the investigation of Theory of Mind."
  ]
}